  <bioghist id="aspace_459518751fa287e32ee9297fcaf4c9fc">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Harry Levin was professor of psychology and dean of the College of Arts and Sciences, Cornell University.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_45734d9032ecb90c01b266b597aa8386">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Personal and professional correspondence, letters of recommendation, student papers, drafts of Levin's books, audiotapes, computer diskettes, professional working papers, and other material documenting his professorship and deanship.</p>  </scopecontent>
